items.title: Suspect charged with attempted murder of New York Jets player Kris Boyd
items.description: A man has been charged with attempted murder in the shooting of New York Jets player Kris Boyd outside a New York City restaurant in November.

items.title: Trump says he'll "make a phone call" to stop Cambodia-Thailand clashes
items.description: President Trump helped end a simmering conflict between Cambodia and Thailand in the summer, but the ceasefire didn't last long.
